DATA VALIDATION SERVICE
The validation service is used to validate the schema of the data. This service calls a set of urls namely https://git.io/vpg9V and https://git.io/vpg95 and validates its responses using a schema provided.
Inorder to validate the schema , please click on the validate button that you find below.
The Result of the validation is
a. Number of objects parsed in the given urls b. Number of null occurences c. Number of occurrences of error
